        @CanIgnoreReturnValue
public WebPushHybridEncrypt.Builder withRecordSize​(int val)
        Sets the record size.

        If set, this value must match the record size set with withRecordSize(int).

        If not set, a record size of 4096 bytes is used. This value should work for most users.

        Sets the public key of the recipient.

        The public key must be formatted as an uncompressed point format, i.e., it has 65 bytes and the first byte must be 0x04.
